  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Batalagoda research on fertilizer application is successful",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Ajantha de Silva, Director General of the Department of Agriculture, said that the research conducted by the Batalagoda Paddy Research Institute of applying 70 percent and 30 percent chemical fertilizers and organic fertilizers for paddy cultivation was successful.",
        "The Batalagoda Paddy Research Institute conducted this research regarding the application of 70 percent chemical fertilizers and 30 percent organic fertilizers to paddy cultivation in the upcoming season.",
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, the entire cultivation process collapsed due to the use of 100% organic fertilizers and liquid fertilizers and the paddy yield fell by 40 percent in the high season of that year."
      ],
